metadata.name: Rural Retreat
metadata.description:
This is my first-ever drone shot. Literally my first click. File name is DJI_0001.dng

In this aerial top-down photo, a farmhouse sits amidst a green field during sunset. The white roof of the farmhouse stands out, while a few agriculture machines dot the landscape. 

A country road, forming the letter T, cuts through the fields. The sun's warm glow casts a serene ambiance, illuminating the farmhouse and highlighting its simplicity. The unpaved road signifies connectivity and the journey of the rural community. 

This captivating scene captures the harmony between nature and human existence, inviting contemplation and appreciation for the beauty of rural life.
